This is the Men's Discipleship Network website.


When switching back and forth to the turn2god.net staging server need to do the following:

1) Change the .htaccess file to point to the appropriate home folder.
2) Make sure that there is a restart.txt file in ~/mdn/current/tmp
3) Make sure you use the deploy.rb script for the correct server


